Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.12,OP,,0,0,0,,大廈的外牆 巨大的銀幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:26.75,OP,,0,0,0,,都會的女神 KISS KISS KISS 對我笑 SO SWEET I FOUND YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:33.60,OP,,0,0,0,,一億個夢 會有十億個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:41.42,OP,,0,0,0,,肯定對的路 NO NO NO沒人會知道 DON'T CHEAT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:50.72,OP,,0,0,0,,迷宮般的道路 只有我與你兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:57.27,OP,,0,0,0,,CARRY ON CARRY ON 嘗試走出一步的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:01:00.78,OP,,0,0,0,,CAN'T STOP IT NO WAY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.85,0:01:03.66,OP,,0,0,0,,CAN'T STOP IT 永遠地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.69,0:01:12.33,OP,,0,0,0,,CAN'T STOP IT 停不下來 HOW CAN YOU HOLD ME ON？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.24,0:01:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,終有一天、必定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,（剛才好險）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的，臭老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,發這種無聊的誓\N（唔？）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,（有什麼意見）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,（就直接說出來）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那個切腹的約定，現在立即去給我取消
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你那亂七八糟的約定竟然把我也扯進去！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.63,0:02:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,（我拒絕）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.23,0:02:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,（男人和熊貓說一不二！）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道你會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我用媽媽的刀來送你一程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,現在立即，在這切開你的肚皮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,（厲…厲害）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起，伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,還要你幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這種小事沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,別跑，別跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,亂子，危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一淋熱水，亂馬變身體質就會被看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:02:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,萬事休已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害，好厲害啊，亂子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,小霞，幫我拿明太子來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃  真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,對了，小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說你是亂馬的未婚妻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這個我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,來，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬他，像個男子漢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,以未婚妻的你來看認為怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼，酷嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼，帥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才一直出現的奇怪停頓是什麼意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬的樣子長得好像伯母你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呢，坐在一起簡直一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,轉換一下話題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼，亂馬的興趣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,興趣好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是格鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是穿女裝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,女裝？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這種沒一點男子氣概的興趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,（是除草啦，太太）\N日文女裝跟除草同音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是那種除草啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了，剛剛我還真不知怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你啊，究竟跟我有什麼仇恨啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我說了不好的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,完完全全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，你真的不想認回你媽媽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要我切腹還不如給小靡勒索比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,勒索？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這是身在福中不知福的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我和小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是想見媽媽，也已經見不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼，小靡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,今次就不用你給我五千日元了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,虧我還一瞬間當真了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,亂子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母，今晚要睡在這房間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然說不能相認
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但你們是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,最少一晚，好好相處一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那個，亂子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,小霞姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,早乙女伯母，說明天就要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,明天要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,突然好像安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，亂馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是說夢話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在夢中，也在找我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼沒長得像個男子漢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好可憐的阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:06:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是做惡夢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是為了伯母，也是為了亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,都不能就這樣讓他們分別
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼，打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然遺憾沒見到亂馬和我丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,請下次再來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,再見伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,再見，亂子也要保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,再見，亂子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真好的熱水啊，亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,洗溫泉啊，樂呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了，亂馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽好像很寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:07:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,而你，竟像是趕走了瘟神般的開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這臭老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這沒辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果沒把你培養成男子漢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,父子倆都要一起切腹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這會痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的，做這麼無聊的約定切什麼腹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,別再嘮嘮叨叨的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起，我忘了東西沒拿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，是伯母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，亂子和熊貓先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在玩水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,請再來玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,再見伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了，小茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我去見媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,現在還說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可是已經約定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這個星期日在公園
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，也想以男性的樣子去見媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我在你眼中究竟是怎樣的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，真有男子漢氣概
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好酷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真的長成了男人中的男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,別讓她知道我的變身體質就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,還有別太美化自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事，不能告訴叔叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,（我聽到了）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,（這樣，到了星期天）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼我…要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不是母親節
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,給伯母的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝，小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,還磨磨蹭蹭幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢，突然這樣有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她認得出我是她兒子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋，竟擔心這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可以見到亂馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,對，亂馬的特徵是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，等等，先別說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很久沒見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但畢竟是我兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我一眼就認出給你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母她等你好久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,從這裡開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我一步也不會讓你過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼也要見媽媽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就先打倒我這爸爸再…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我是為了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,為了你好才會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,假如，亂馬！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,明明要以男人姿態跟媽媽相認
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那時候卻偏偏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在潑水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就算小心避過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,地下水管突然爆裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不會啦，那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,即使那也能避開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,偶然路過的賣金魚的人突然跌倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那種事不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你不明白我是在避免你去切腹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,（亂馬不會來的，太太）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,（亂馬不會來的，太太）\N（這就行了）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,叔叔\N（哇…！）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,（啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,終於到了嗎，亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,（糟了）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,長得真像你爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母，不是啦不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜，你來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那個，亂馬長得完全不像叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，先別說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很久沒見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但畢竟是我兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,今次我一定能一眼認出給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,（啊，亂馬）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？在哪在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.07,0:13:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母，亂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,被叔叔…帶走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,竟敢這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,等著我吧，媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定能找到你，跟你相認的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,還擺什麼姿勢啦，在那邊在那邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,（那邊，那邊）\N哪裡，哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡，老爸那混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬不來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,（怎麼也好）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,（暴露身份的話就要切腹啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不暴露身份就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽，現在就讓你看看我男子漢的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這…這是男孩子的手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，亂馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,亂子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了，伯母？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起，我認錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,（呼…）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,（太太真的那麼想見亂馬嗎？）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,想見，現在就想立即見到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,（嘿嘿，那麼…）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你想幹什麼，熊貓？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,（想要命的話就快走）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,（啊！）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你要這樣我也不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母，到外邊去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事，小茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,用這樣下流的手段，混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，是不是不想見我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:15:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可是，等了這樣久他還不出現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,出是出現了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你這卑鄙傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哼，有什麼好囂張的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你不也一樣怕切腹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.73,0:16:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你有切開肚皮的覺悟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,總而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想讓媽媽看一下男子漢的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸你就閉嘴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,還是說，想見我也不敢見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,難道亂馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有長成個男子漢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會，這不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了，亂子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.09,0:17:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這種，只充一時的謊話\N遲早會被拆穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,反而只會讓媽媽傷心而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說你怕切腹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,（這才是我的兒子）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我…要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定，亂馬已長成為堂堂正正的男子漢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母我相信著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我多管閒事，對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因為伯母，是那麼的想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而我，卻只想看看她高興的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不過切腹也真是可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不是在逼你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你這不是正在逼我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我好想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,（放水按鈕，別坐）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,溫泉噴出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是鐳元素溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,亂…馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:18:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看到我真正的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽她…一定很失望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你很有男子氣概啊，亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,亂子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是亂子救我的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,原來那是夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬來救我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣子真是太有男子漢氣概了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我，見到亂馬了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,伯母，那其實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了，現在就讓她當是夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼，再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,終有一天，到我會變真正的男人為止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的夢，請你一定要記住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸，叔叔，茶放在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你，小霞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,經常麻煩你，真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，卑鄙這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,早乙女兄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼總是這樣逃避問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.26,0:20:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我其實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:20:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真是很喜歡你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,笨死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你這是什麼眼光！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我們出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,慢走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要遲到了，亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道啦，煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼，小茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:58.89,ED,,0,0,0,,留在我身邊 近得可以四目相投
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:03.14,ED,,0,0,0,,可是溫柔和笑臉卻交錯而過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:07.33,ED,,0,0,0,,你裝作沒發覺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.50,0:22:11.76,ED,,0,0,0,,又趕著去惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.78,0:22:20.22,ED,,0,0,0,,即使如此 在那閃爍的山丘上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:35.63,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fsp1\pos(280,389.333)}斷斷續續的故事 只是單純的演戲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:35.63,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fsp1\pos(366.667,472)}包裹著兩人的彩虹 能實現一個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.65,0:22:43.45,ED,,0,0,0,,有太陽的氣味呢 無論是你的夢想 還是你的襯衫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.52,0:22:52.37,ED,,0,0,0,,充滿希望的眼睛 能把一切都變輝煌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:23:00.97,ED,,0,0,0,,所以最重要的夢想 千萬別放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.73,0:23:10.10,ED,,0,0,0,,只要一直保有飛向天空的力量和勇氣
